nodes.text: Mon Calamari Subworks was a Mon Calamari company that produced a number of distinct submarines, with the Keelkana-class attack submersible being one of the company's greatest triumphs. Each Keelkana-class vessel was unique in some small way, with the variations reflecting Mon Calamari aesthetic values.
Mon Calamari Subworks was first mentioned in the 2020 Fantasy Flight Games Star Wars Roleplaying supplement, Starships and Speeders.
